text: Kathryn Prescott (born 4 June 1991) is an English actress. She is best known for playing Emily Fitch on the teen drama television series Skins and Carter Stevens in the 2014 MTV drama Finding Carter. Prescott was born in London. Her career began in 2008. On 9 September 2021, Prescott was hit by a cement truck while crossing the road in New York City.
